Text: you must be kidding... all i have in my wallet for them is a middle finger up!

Informative, but it doesn't say what you can do about it.
There isn't a whole lot you CAN do about it. You can try paying for a VPN service or a seedbox, but it's just another set they have to follow, and one with your financial details all over it.
